---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Three Steps. Zero Chasing.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex gap-6 sm:gap-10 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-forest text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-slate-200 mt-4"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Connect your client list</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Upload your client list and connect your WhatsApp Business account. Takes less than 10 minutes. No migration needed.</p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-forest bg-forest-pale px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
            10 minutes to set up
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="flex gap-6 sm:gap-10 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-forest text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-slate-200 mt-4"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">JOHN takes over</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">JOHN messages each client on WhatsApp, asks for specific documents, follows up automatically, and categorizes everything that comes in.</p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-forest bg-forest-pale px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
            Fully autonomous
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex gap-6 sm:gap-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-forest text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0">3</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Documents in your dashboard</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Every document lands organized in your dashboard — categorized by client, type, and tax year. Ready for filing, exportable in one click.</p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-forest bg-forest-pale px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
            Organized & exportable
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
